WEBVTT

00:00:01.500 --> 00:00:05.098
when in the course of human events it

00:00:04.370 --> 00:00:07.690
becomes necessary for one people to

00:00:07.799 --> 00:00:09.450
dissolve the political bands which have

00:00:09.689 --> 00:00:11.267
connected them with another and to

00:00:11.449 --> 00:00:14.578
assume among the powers of the earth the

00:00:14.269 --> 00:00:17.740
separate and equal station to which the

00:00:17.579 --> 00:00:19.287
laws of nature and of nature's God

00:00:19.739 --> 00:00:22.349
entitle them a decent respect to the

00:00:22.289 --> 00:00:25.300
opinions of mankind requires that they

00:00:25.350 --> 00:00:27.569
should declare the causes which impel

00:00:27.300 --> 00:00:30.880
them to the separation we hold these

00:00:30.570 --> 00:00:32.980
truths to be self-evident that all men

00:00:32.880 --> 00:00:34.420
are created equal that they are endowed

00:00:34.979 --> 00:00:36.358
by their creator with certain

00:00:36.420 --> 00:00:39.059
unalienable rights that among these are

00:00:39.359 --> 00:00:43.628
life liberty and the pursuit of happiness